snippet.title: Great Hero's Beard Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming October 4th to Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/935270/Great_Heros_Beard/

Start your journey as a simple soy-boi and watch as you grow a big-ass warlord's beard, slay a bunch of demigods & rescue thicc girls who will show their gratitude and bear offspring. Never stop looting.
